description:
Adam Savage explains the core design differences between Star Wars and Star Trek ship modelling. While they may seem similar at first glance, the narratives behind them are completely different.

Did you know Adam worked in ILM while they were making Star Wars Episodes I and II?
title: Are Star Wars and Star Trek the same?
